## HOUSE PRICE PREDICTION
This project predicts house prices using Regression

## TECHNOLOGIES USED
-Python
-Pandas
-Matplotlib
-Scikit-learn

## MECHINE LEARNING CONCEPTS USED
-Linear Regression
-Data preprocessing
-Missing values handling
-Feature scaling
-Train-test split
-Prediction on new data
-Regression plotting,scattering
-R2-score

## OUTPUT
Predicts house price based on area

## RUN LOCALLY
pip install -r requirement.txt

python linearreg.py

python -m streamlit run app.py